Author: killvourdarlings
Text: Thank you. Any support honestly means a lot because ultimately I know I need to do this but it sucks a whole lot and I hate the dentist anyway. Ugh. But you're right it'll pay off in the future. Better to get a check up and resolve any problems now if there are any!

Author: bitter-kittens
Text: I'm proud of you for going to the dentist and prioritizing your health & teeth. It is so frustrating that it is hard to find new dentists when you need one so I hope this pays off in the future.
